Matching Patterns to Algorithms
If the problem mentions... 	Try this algorithm...
"Substring", "Occurrences", "Pattern"	KMP or Rabin-Karp
"Prefix which is also a Suffix"	LPS Table (KMP Preprocessing)
"Duplicates", "Repeated chunks", "Hashes"	Rabin-Karp (Rolling Hash)
"Prefix Tree", "Dictionary search"	Trie
